data.description: This fantastic 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home has been completely updated in the past 6 years! This home features 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, main floor laundry, basement for storage, and is ready for new owners! The furnace, central air conditioning, water heater, some electrical wiring and plumbing were updated ONLY 6 years ago! The exterior of the home features maintenance free vinyl siding, updated landscaping and sidewalks, new garage roof, and 6 year old house roof! The huge detached 2 car garage has alley access, and there is a private patio area between the garage and the house. This house sits on a large lot, and also comes with a large storage shed. If you are looking for an updated home that is move-in ready, you will definitely want to consider 911 Pulaski Street, Lincoln!
